title: The Market Juicery
typeOfFood: Lacto, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Smoothie and juice bar in the Tip Top Arcade. In addition to smoothies and cold-pressed juices the kitchen also makes wraps and sandwiches, which are displayed in a deli case. Not vegan but you could ask the staff to make a wrap/sandwich vegan for you. Has raw vegan desserts.
